Python
# Pseudo-code
def calculate_npc_price(item_id):
    current_supply = get_total_supply(item_id)
    demand_rate = get_demand_rate(item_id)  # S·ªë l∆∞·ª£ng giao d·ªãch/ng√†y
    
    # Base price t·ª´ database
    base_price = get_base_price(item_id)
    
    # Dynamic multiplier d·ª±a tr√™n supply/demand
    if current_supply > demand_rate * 7:  # D∆∞ th·ª´a 7 ng√†y
        multiplier = 0.7  # Gi·∫£m gi√° 30%
    elif current_supply < demand_rate * 2:  # Thi·∫øu h·ª•t
        multiplier = 1.3  # TƒÉng gi√° 30%
    else:
        multiplier = 1.0
    
    npc_buy_price = base_price * multiplier * 0.8  # NPC mua th·∫•p h∆°n 20%
    npc_sell_price = base_price * multiplier * 1.2  # NPC b√°n cao h∆°n 20%
    
    return npc_buy_price, npc_sell_price
V√≠ d·ª• th·ª±c t·∫ø:
Code
Iron Ore base price: 0.5 E Token/kg

T√¨nh hu·ªëng 1: Qu√° nhi·ªÅu ng∆∞·ªùi ƒë√†o Iron Ore
‚Üí Supply: 100,000 kg/ng√†y
‚Üí Demand: 50,000 kg/ng√†y
‚Üí D∆∞ th·ª´a 2x
‚Üí NPC buy price: 0.5 x 0.7 x 0.8 = 0.28 E Token/kg ‚Üì
‚Üí Miners th·∫•y gi√° th·∫•p ‚Üí chuy·ªÉn sang ƒë√†o Titanium
‚Üí Supply Iron gi·∫£m ‚Üí gi√° tƒÉng d·∫ßn

T√¨nh hu·ªëng 2: √çt ng∆∞·ªùi ƒë√†o Iron Ore (v√¨ event Sao H·∫£i V∆∞∆°ng)
‚Üí Supply: 20,000 kg/ng√†y
