10.3.3. Dynamic Quest Rewards
H·ªá th·ªëng t·ª± ƒë·ªông ƒëi·ªÅu ch·ªânh ph·∫ßn th∆∞·ªüng quest:
Python
def calculate_quest_reward(quest_type):
    token_inflation_rate = get_inflation_rate()  # % token m·ªõi/ng√†y
    active_players = get_active_players_24h()
    
    # Base reward
    base_reward = 20 E Token
    
    # N·∫øu inflation cao ‚Üí gi·∫£m reward
    if token_inflation_rate > 30:  # >30%/th√°ng
        multiplier = 0.75
    elif token_inflation_rate < 10:  # <10%/th√°ng
        multiplier = 1.25
    else:
        multiplier = 1.0
    
    # N·∫øu qu√° nhi·ªÅu ng∆∞·ªùi ch∆°i ‚Üí gi·∫£m reward (tr√°nh l·∫°m ph√°t)
    if active_players > 5000:
        player_multiplier = 0.9
    else:
        player_multiplier = 1.0
    
    final_reward = base_reward * multiplier * player_multiplier
    return final_reward
10.3.4. Auto Burn Rate Adjustment
Burn rate t·ª± ƒë·ªông tƒÉng/gi·∫£m theo inflation:
Python
def calculate_burn_rate(transaction_type):
    token_circulation = get_total_tokens_in_circulation()
    token_created_30d = get_tokens_created_last_30_days()
    inflation_rate = (token_created_30d / token_circulation) * 100
    
    # Base burn rates
    base_rates = {
        'fuel': 0.30,
        'repair': 0.50,
        'craft': 0.40,
        'marketplace_tax': 0.20
    }
    
    # Adjust burn rate based on inflation
    if inflation_rate > 30:  # L·∫°m ph√°t cao
        multiplier = 1.5  # TƒÉng burn l√™n 50%
    elif inflation_rate < 10:  # Deflation
        multiplier = 0.8  # Gi·∫£m burn 20%
    else:
        multiplier = 1.0
    
    return base_rates[transaction_type] * multiplier
V√≠ d·ª•:
Code
T√¨nh hu·ªëng: L·∫°m ph√°t 35%/th√°ng (qu√° cao)

Fuel burn rate:
- Base: 30%
- New: 30% x 1.5 = 45% ‚Üë

‚Üí M·ªói l·∫ßn mua fuel, 45% token b·ªã burn thay v√¨ 30%
‚Üí Supply token gi·∫£m nhanh h∆°n
‚Üí Inflation gi·∫£m v·ªÅ 25-30%
‚Üí System t·ª± ƒëi·ªÅu ch·ªânh burn rate v·ªÅ 30-35%
